name: Le Shoot 'Em Up
description:
Le' Shoot Em up
Fast paced arcade shooter. Will we see you in the leaderobards?

This game was made back in 2016

Simple arcade shooter. Get the best possible score before time runs out. If your one of the top 10 players your score and chosen username will be showcased in the leaderboards for all to see.

Targets:
Green = don't thoost!
Red = shoot!
Brown, Black and Yellow = head shots

Play in full screen mode for best experience.
